hostResourcesTypesModule.organization: IETF Host Resources MIB Working Group
hostResourcesTypesModule.contactinfo: Steve Waldbusser Postal: Lucent Technologies, Inc. 1213 Innsbruck Dr. Sunnyvale, CA 94089 USA Phone: 650-318-1251 Fax: 650-318-1633 Email: waldbusser@ins.com In addition, the Host Resources MIB mailing list is dedicated to discussion of this MIB. hostResourcesTypesModule.description: This MIB module registers type definitions for storage types, device types, and file system types. After the initial revision, this module will be maintained by IANA.

hrStorageOther.name: hrStorageOther
hrStorageOther.description: The storage type identifier used when no other defined type is appropriate.

hrStorageRam.name: hrStorageRam
hrStorageRam.description: The storage type identifier used for RAM.

hrStorageVirtualMemory.name: hrStorageVirtualMemory
hrStorageVirtualMemory.description: The storage type identifier used for virtual memory, temporary storage of swapped or paged memory.

hrStorageFixedDisk.name: hrStorageFixedDisk
hrStorageFixedDisk.description: The storage type identifier used for non-removable rigid rotating magnetic storage devices.

hrStorageRemovableDisk.name: hrStorageRemovableDisk
hrStorageRemovableDisk.description: The storage type identifier used for removable rigid rotating magnetic storage devices.

hrStorageFloppyDisk.name: hrStorageFloppyDisk
hrStorageFloppyDisk.description: The storage type identifier used for non-rigid rotating magnetic storage devices.

hrStorageCompactDisc.name: hrStorageCompactDisc
hrStorageCompactDisc.description: The storage type identifier used for read-only rotating optical storage devices.

hrStorageRamDisk.name: hrStorageRamDisk
hrStorageRamDisk.description: The storage type identifier used for a file system that is stored in RAM.

hrStorageFlashMemory.name: hrStorageFlashMemory
hrStorageFlashMemory.description: The storage type identifier used for flash memory.

hrStorageNetworkDisk.name: hrStorageNetworkDisk
hrStorageNetworkDisk.description: The storage type identifier used for a networked file system.

hrDeviceOther.name: hrDeviceOther
hrDeviceOther.description: The device type identifier used when no other defined type is appropriate.

hrDeviceUnknown.name: hrDeviceUnknown
hrDeviceUnknown.description: The device type identifier used when the device type is unknown.

hrDeviceProcessor.name: hrDeviceProcessor
hrDeviceProcessor.description: The device type identifier used for a CPU.

hrDeviceDiskStorage.name: hrDeviceDiskStorage

hrDeviceKeyboard.name: hrDeviceKeyboard

hrDeviceModem.name: hrDeviceModem
hrDeviceModem.description: The device type identifier used for a modem.

hrDeviceParallelPort.name: hrDeviceParallelPort
hrDeviceParallelPort.description: The device type identifier used for a parallel port.

hrDevicePointing.name: hrDevicePointing
hrDevicePointing.description: The device type identifier used for a pointing device (e.g., a mouse).

hrDeviceNonVolatileMemory.description: The device type identifier used for a non-volatile memory storage device.
